            <title>[SYNAPSE-182] POJOCommand mediator should set the properties back to the message after the execution</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-182</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;POJOCommand mediator only set the properties to the Command object before starting the execution. We should support setting the properties back to the message from the command after execution.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
